        "name": "Rapid Retreat",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You know how to swiftly escape from harm. You instantly teleport out of danger into an unoccupied space within range, and you gain resistance to all damage against the triggering damage equal to your level. You can\u2019t Cast this Spell if there\u2019s no space to move into.",
